[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0010","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 DNS Message 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 及 8 版本中的 DNS 消息处理组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的恶意 DNS 查询消息，利用消息解析过程中的缺陷触发服务崩溃，导致 DNS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响大量使用上述版本 BIND 的 DNS 服务器，攻击者通过发送精心构造的 DNS 请求报文即可实施攻击，无需复杂前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0010"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.340","remediation":"升级至 BIND 8.2 或更高版本以修复 DNS 消息解析缺陷；BIND 4.9/8 系列已停止维护，建议迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列并升级到 ISC 发布的最新稳定版（如 9.18.x 或 9.20.x）。如暂无法升级，应在边界防火墙上限制外部 DNS 查询来源 IP 并启用递归查询访问控制列表以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0043","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0404","title":"SmartMax MailMax SMTP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 的 SMTP 服务组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统 SMTP 端口发送特制的超长请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台下的 MailMax SMTP 服务器 1.0 版本，攻击复杂度低，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0404"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.490","remediation":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 已停止维护，官方不再提供安全补丁。建议立即升级或迁移至仍在积极维护的邮件服务器，如 hMailServer、MailEnable 或 Windows Server SMTP 服务。如无法立即迁移，应在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 SMTP 端口（TCP 25），并部署入侵检测系统监控异常 SMTP 流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0404","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20600"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0041","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0387","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 凭据缓存机制信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows 95 和 Windows 98 系统中存在旧版凭据缓存机制缺陷，该机制以明文形式存储网络密码，导致本地攻击者能够读取并获取用户的明文网络凭据，进而利用窃取的凭据进行横向移动或权限提升。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 及 Windows 98 操作系统，攻击者需具备本地访问权限方可利用。CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0387"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:17.277","remediation":"由于 Windows 95/98 已停止支持且无官方补丁，建议立即升级至 Windows 10/11 或仍受支持的企业版系统。临时缓解措施：在注册表中禁用凭据缓存（HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Policies\\Network，将 DisablePasswordCaching 设为 1），并将系统置于隔离网络段，限制外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ168115","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/829","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-052"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0039","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0039.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0007","title":"OpenSSL PKCS#1 填充加密会话信息泄露漏洞","description":"该漏洞由贝尔实验室研究员 Daniel Bleichenbacher 于 1998 年发现，涉及 SSL 协议中 RSA PKCS #1 v1.5 填充方式的侧信道攻击。远程攻击者首先截获客户端与服务器之间的加密 SSL 会话，随后向服务器发送约一百万个精心构造的密文，通过观察服务器返回的填充校验错误差异逐步推断出会话密钥，最终解密被截获的加密通信内容。该漏洞影响 SSLeay 加密库及使用 SSL 协议的大量产品，包括 Microsoft Internet Information Server 3.0/4.0、Netscape Enterprise Server、Exchange Server 5.5 等服务器软件。由于攻击需要大量交互查询，服务器 CPU 和网络流量异常上升可作为检测手段。Microsoft 已于安全公告 MS98-002 中发布修补程序更新 SCHANNEL.dll。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0007"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:19.650","remediation":"立即将 SSLeay 升级至 OpenSSL 0.9.6 或更新版本，该版本修复了 PKCS #1 填充预言机信息泄露缺陷。如无法升级，在服务端禁用 SSLv2 协议，仅启用 TLS 1.0+，并配置统一的错误返回消息以防止攻击者通过错误响应区分填充格式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-002"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0039.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0037","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0382","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 屏幕保护程序权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 的屏幕保护程序在切换安全上下文时未正确验证权限变更状态，导致本地攻击者可通过特殊操作利用该漏洞以提升的权限运行任意程序。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 NT 3.5.1 全系列服务包版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0382"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.647","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 或更高版本，该更新修复了屏幕保护程序未正确验证安全上下文的问题。如无法升级，可禁用屏幕保护程序（控制面板→显示→屏幕保护程序→选择\"无\"），并要求用户在离开时手动锁定工作站（Ctrl+Alt+Del→锁定工作站）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-008","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0382","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0382.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9h86-j86m-7fx3/GHSA-9h86-j86m-7fx3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--284f3c9d-c5aa-4a6f-9d77-395fb3b2fa10.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0037.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0036","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0036.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0381","title":"Super syslog 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Super 3.11.6 及之前版本的 syslog 工具中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 syslog 发送特制的日志消息触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Debian 2.0 等使用 super 3.11.6 的 Linux 发行版，利用前提是攻击者具备本地系统访问权限，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0381"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.503","remediation":"升级 super 包至 3.12 及以上版本，该版本已修复 syslog 函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。临时缓解措施可移除 super 程序的 setuid 权限位：chmod u-s /usr/bin/super，限制非授权用户提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/342","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.3.96.990225011801.12757A-100000%40eleet","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19270"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0036.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0035","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0380","title":"SLMail 远程管理服务 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"SLMail 3.1 及 3.2 版本在启用远程管理服务（RAS）时存在不安全的文件访问漏洞。本地攻击者可将用户的 Finger 文件路径设置为指向任意目标文件，然后执行 finger 命令读取该文件内容，从而访问 NTFS 文件系统中的任意文件。该漏洞源于 SLMail 对 Finger 服务中文件路径处理不当，导致权限验证缺失，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0380"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.370","remediation":"升级 SLMail 至 4.0 或更新版本，该版本已修复 Finger File 路径遍历漏洞；如无法升级，禁用 Remote Administration Service (RAS) 组件，并限制本地用户对 Finger File 配置的写入权限。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 finger 服务或通过防火墙阻止 finger 端口 (79/TCP) 的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91996412724720&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91999015212415&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92110501504997&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/497","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/5392"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0034","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0379","title":"Microsoft Taskpads 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft BackOffice Resource Kit 中的 Taskpads 组件将某些 COM 方法错误标记为\"对脚本安全\"，远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用 Internet Explorer 中的脚本引擎调用这些危险方法，在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98/NT 等系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0379"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.247","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-007 提供的补丁，该补丁会移除存在安全风险的 Taskpads 功能。受影响用户（安装了 Windows 98 Resource Kit、Windows 98 Resource Kit Sampler 或 BackOffice Resource Kit 第二版的用户）应通过 Microsoft Download Center 获取并安装对应补丁。如无法安装补丁，可手动删除 Taskpads 相关组件或避免在安装有上述 Resource Kit 的机器上浏览网页作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1019","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/498","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-007","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0379.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0379","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0379.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0379.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vmvm-9v9v-pm58/GHSA-vmvm-9v9v-pm58.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0379.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/backoffice_resource_kit_cve.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000544.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0034.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0032","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0032.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0378","title":"Trend Micro InterScan VirusWall for Solaris 双GET请求病毒扫描绕过漏洞","description":"Trend Micro InterScan VirusWall for Solaris 存在病毒扫描绕过漏洞。当攻击者向受保护的 Web 服务器发送包含两个 GET 命令的单个 HTTP 请求时，该安全网关无法正确解析请求结构，导致第二个 GET 请求所指向的文件绕过病毒扫描直接通过。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞上传或传输包含恶意代码的文件，从而绕过安全检测机制，对目标系统造成潜在危害。该漏洞影响 InterScan VirusWall for Solaris 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0378"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.117","remediation":"升级 InterScan VirusWall 至 3.01 及以上版本，该版本已修复单 HTTP 请求中双 GET 命令绕过病毒扫描的问题。如无法升级，建议在 Web 服务器前部署反向代理或 WAF，过滤异常 HTTP 请求格式。该产品已停止支持，建议迁移至 Trend Micro 当前支持的网关安全产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6167","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0378.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0378","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0378.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0378.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9fhp-rxc4-x67h/GHSA-9fhp-rxc4-x67h.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0378.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82471/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000543.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0032.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0031","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0377","title":"Oracle Solaris INETD 进程表拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Unix 系统存在进程表攻击漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发起大量网络服务连接请求，耗尽系统进程表资源，导致系统无法接受新的连接请求，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需认证即可实施攻击，影响各类 Unix 操作系统。攻击者只需建立大量并发连接即可触发，属于典型的资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0377"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.993","remediation":"建议将 inetd 替换为 xinetd，并在配置中添加连接速率限制，如 `cps = 25 30` 和 `per_source = 5`；同时通过 `/etc/system` 或 `ulimit` 调大系统进程表上限（如 `max_nprocs`），并使用 TCP Wrappers（`/etc/hosts.allow`）限制仅允许可信来源 IP 连接网络服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securitytracker.com/id/1033881","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0377.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0377","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0377.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0377.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w9p9-j3v6-q4vf/GHSA-w9p9-j3v6-q4vf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0377.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x78000/77236/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000542.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0009","title":"ISC BIND 反向查询远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC BIND（Berkeley Internet Name Domain）4.9 及 8.x 版本存在反向查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的反向查询请求，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 4.9 及 8.x 的多种操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商建议立即升级至不受影响的版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0009"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.137","remediation":"立即升级 BIND 至 8.2 或更高版本，或在条件允许时迁移至 BIND 9 系列（如 9.3.0+），因为 8.2 已修复逆查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 named.conf 中禁用 `inverse-query` 选项以临时缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/134","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19112","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0009","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0009.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/252.txt","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/McAfeeNSM/Integrations/McAfeeNSMv2/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/deleted.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bind_iquery.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0374","title":"Debian GNU/Linux cfengine 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 发行版中的 cfengine 软件包存在符号链接攻击漏洞。cfengine 是一款基于主机的配置管理工具，通常以 root 权限运行。由于其在处理临时文件时未充分验证符号链接的真实性，拥有本地账户权限的攻击者可通过在可写目录中创建恶意符号链接（指向 /etc/shadow 等系统关键文件），诱导 cfengine 以 root 权限错误地读取或覆写目标文件，导致敏感信息泄露或系统完整性破坏。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0374"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.563","remediation":"建议升级 cfengine 至 1.5.4 及以上版本，该版本修复了临时文件创建中的符号链接跟随漏洞。使用 cfengine 管理文件时避免将临时文件写入公共可写目录（如 /tmp），或使用专属临时目录并设置 umask 077 限制访问权限。在 Debian 系统中及时应用 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade 保持软件包更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0374"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0025","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0359","title":"Marc Schaefer ptylogin 拒绝服务及密码泄露漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中的 ptylogin 工具存在访问控制缺陷，本地用户可通过操纵伪终端设备锁定调制解调器，导致合法用户无法拨入（拒绝服务）；亦可利用该缺陷以调制解调器身份向外拨号，或截获拨入用户的登录密码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响所有使用 ptylogin 管理串行拨号会话的 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限即可实施攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0359"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.617","remediation":"立即升级 ptylogin 至最新安全版本；同时移除 ptylogin 二进制文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ptylogin），并将可执行权限限制为仅授权用户组。对调制解调器设备文件（/dev/ttyS*、/dev/modem）设置 600 权限，仅允许 root 和拨号用户组访问。实施回拨认证机制作为临时缓解措施，并建议用 SSH 或 VPN 替代基于调制解调器的远程接入方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0359.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82482/info.html","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0023","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0317","title":"Linux su 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux su 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 su 程序传递特制的长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而将普通用户权限提升至 root 超级管理员权限。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本中的 su 组件，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，一旦成功可完全控制目标系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0317"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.383","remediation":"立即升级 shadow-utils（shadow）软件包至最新版本，所有现代 Linux 发行版均已修复此漏洞。Red Hat 系执行 `yum update shadow-utils`，Debian 系执行 `apt-get update && apt-get install --only-upgrade shadow`。如无法升级，限制非授权用户的本地 shell 访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0317"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0023.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0022","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0005","title":"Netscape Messaging Server 与 UW IMAPD 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Messaging Server 3.55 及 University of Washington imapd 10.234 的 IMAP 服务存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 IMAP 服务的 authenticate 命令发送特制超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，进而以 IMAP 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响大量使用相关 IMAP 软件的邮件服务器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0005"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.900","remediation":"University of Washington imapd 10.234 用户应立即升级至 11.xx 及以上版本；Netscape Messaging Server 3.55 用户应升级至 4.0 或更新版本。建议在无法立即升级时，限制 IMAP 服务的源 IP 访问范围，或在不影响业务的情况下临时禁用 IMAP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/177","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/130","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19107","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0005.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0005.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-p